ps1

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • ps1.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an implementation of a contact entry. It contains the following attributes:
    • Id: int
    • Name: String
    • Postal Address: String
    • Phone Number: String
    • Email Address: String
    • Note: String

    Attribute Name is required for an entry, while others are optional. Id is auto incremental and is the discriminative tag for an Entry.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Guang Yang
